      "content": "that's a good start with the atmosphere. i want to get more specific with the people in the scene though. as the protagonist walks down this street, i want to see the types of people that make them feel like they're in over their heads. what kind of people are hanging out on the corners or watching from the doorways? give me some character descriptions that really drive home that sense of threat and lawlessness.",
